blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300469c60902c261344d9a7bb1122be0adb4b3e2","tid":272510,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>主力買野定純行下先？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去行新宿不如行埋池袋？或者去埋明治神宮行埋佢？<br />\n<br />\n去上野+淺草去埋下町睇skytree&amp;阿美橫町買藥妝?</blockquote><br />\n明治神宮Day2會去呀<br />\n依家諗住唔去動物園 去阿美橫町</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿美橫町無野行架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係WO 都算有D野行下 有幾條街 有野食有野買<br />\n有D似女人街咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46acb29d5af8f0d8f5c3c89a5be59736f0174bd1","tid":272510,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"諗住買3days pass 但唔知邊到買<br />\n係平和島 去 東新宿 中途有冇地方買<br />\n機場果邊又唔係24小時有得買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f154dfa2b5043edcfd0ceb90f86c6b7c0375ef15","tid":272510,"uid":29101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住買3days pass 但唔知邊到買<br />\n係平和島 去 東新宿 中途有冇地方買<br />\n機場果邊又唔係24小時有得買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係地鐵站/機場都買到 啲機有中英日同好多唔同語言 <br />\n至於買邊種就睇你點玩<br />\n如果去啲地方會經常轉搭metro/jr等等就買互通個隻，因為基本上好近既站eg1-2分鐘車程最平都好似140en左右1人（唔太記得幾en）所以如果去得chur又成日轉地點可考慮下"},{"pid":"0e948343058b00d31493517f24f700e240f25fba","tid":272510,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><b